&lt;p&gt;Oddball believes that the best products are built when companies understand and value the things they are working on. We value learning and growth and the ability to make a big impact at a small company. We believe that we can make big changes happen and improve the daily lives of millions of people by bringing quality software to the federal space.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for a &lt;strong&gt;Golang&amp;nbsp;Engineer&lt;/strong&gt; to join our CMS team, building and maintaining the APIs and backend services that power Healthcare.gov tools used by millions of Americans enrolling in and exploring health coverage — including third party enrollment platforms.&lt;/p&gt;
