&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with &lt;strong&gt;AWS&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;ECS&lt;/strong&gt; and federal security and compliance requirements is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with containerized applications like &lt;strong&gt;Docker &lt;/strong&gt;is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Thrives in a remote, collaborative &lt;strong&gt;Agile&lt;/strong&gt; environment and genuinely enjoys working closely with a cross-functional team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicates clearly and openly, whether in a code review or a cross-team planning session&lt;/li&gt;
